    "content": "`A = sqrt(12) + sqrt(27) - sqrt(3)`\r\n`A = sqrt(4) . sqrt(3) + sqrt(9) . sqrt(3) - sqrt(3)`\r\n`A = 2sqrt(3) + 3sqrt(3) - sqrt(3)`\r\n`A = (2 + 3 - 1)sqrt(3)`\r\n`A = 4sqrt(3)`",
